phone with Dr. Van Lowe.

240
00:18:40.386 --> 00:18:41.410
Oh?

241
00:18:42.088 --> 00:18:46.184
And he told me a few
things I found very interesting.

242
00:18:47.393 --> 00:18:49.055
Like what?

243
00:18:51.530 --> 00:18:55.524
He told me he gave you a list of
things to do to lower your blood pressure.

244
00:18:55.701 --> 00:18:57.499
Is that right?

245
00:18:58.871 --> 00:19:01.102
Well. there could
have been a list.

246
00:19:02.108 --> 00:19:04.168
Reduce your salt intake.

247
00:19:04.343 --> 00:19:06.938
Start a low-fat.
low-cholesterol diet.

248
00:19:07.113 --> 00:19:08.911
Exercise every day.

249
00:19:09.081 --> 00:19:13.451
And that stupid "One. Two.
Three" poem wasn't even on the list!

250
00:19:15.755 --> 00:19:19.658
I found the booklet in the waiting room.
It was keeping the coffee table level.

251
00:19:20.693 --> 00:19:23.561
Carl. why did you ignore
the doctor's advice?

252
00:19:24.697 --> 00:19:29.795
Oh. come on. Harriette. No
salt. no donuts. lots of exercise.

253
00:19:29.969 --> 00:19:32.097
My life will be a living hell.

254
00:19:34.774 --> 00:19:37.266
At least you'd be living.

255
00:19:37.443 --> 00:19:39.071
I know.

256
00:19:39.245 --> 00:19:41.009
Listen. Carl.

257
00:19:41.180 --> 00:19:43.706
You may not worry about
your health. but I sure do...

258
00:19:43.883 --> 00:19:45.749
and so does the
rest of your family.

259
00:19:46.285 --> 00:19:50.655
But. Harriette. the stuff the
doc wants me to do is a real pain.

260
00:19:52.124 --> 00:19:54.559
I'll tell you what
gives me a pain. Carl.

261
00:19:55.394 --> 00:19:57.863
The thought of
living without you.

262
00:19:58.631 --> 00:20:00.657
Oh. Harriette.

263
00:20:00.833 --> 00:20:04.235
Carl. we have a lot
to look forward to.

264
00:20:04.403 --> 00:20:07.805
I want both of us to be here
to watch our children grow up...

265
00:20:07.973 --> 00:20:10.568
and get married and
have children of their own.

266
00:20:13.012 --> 00:20:15.277
Would be nice to
have some grandkids.

267
00:20:15.448 --> 00:20:16.780
Yeah.

268
00:20:17.783 --> 00:20:19.843
We're a team. Carl.

269
00:20:20.019 --> 00:20:23.012
Let's do everything we can
to keep this team together.

270
00:20:25.091 --> 00:20:27.253
You're right. sweetheart.

271
00:20:27.426 --> 00:20:30.919
You know. Robert
Browning said it best.

272
00:20:31.864 --> 00:20:36.825
<i>Grow old along with
me The best is yet to be</i>

273
00:20:38.170 --> 00:20:39.866
I love you. Carl.

274
00:20:40.039 --> 00:20:41.803
I love you too. Harriette.

274
